Create a .md or text file and past the PlantUML code used to create the Diagram
Always Update the source code for the diagram in the text file, when making changes to the diagram so that other people can easily edit it later if needed

!IMPORTANT!  
There should always be at least one text file for the PlantUML code and one file for the diagram itself
You dont have to replace old diagrams, ust name the newer or latest ones as _v1 or _v2, etc. 
